node.text:
LIQUID GOLD👑
I couldn’t be more excited to announce the new LIQUID GOLD protein flavor that @1upnutrition and I have created! This protein is 138 calories, 25g protein, 5g carbs, and 2g fat. The flavor is a mixture of vanilla graham cracker with a hint of lemon….and also includes…edible gold glitter inside!🤣👏
We’ve been working on this flavor/concept for a while now and when I first tasted it the flavor was just WOW… We truly found liquid gold! We can’t wait for you to try this new flavor! What other flavors should we do in the future?💛
This limited edition protein will be launching in one week: Thursday, August 19th at 11 am CST! Use code BUFFBUNNY to get 20% off and free domestic shipping!
Should I do a giveaway with the protein?!😄
